snippet.title: Angry Penguin - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
do you like Super Mario 64, Crash bandicoot, Banjo Kazooie or even Spyro ?
Those are good game, but a bit easy ngl
Discover ANGRY PENGUIN, a challenging platformer with numerous and very hard trials, Inspired by games like AltF4, A Difficult Game About Climbing, Only Up or Getting Over It !
Help him recover his eggs and discover the secrets of the first map: The Abandoned Island
(if you are a pro player, you can try to speed run the game. But it's difficult, i warned you)
WISH LIST ON COMMENT
